==TSR 2003 – ''Dungeons & Dragons Supplement I: Greyhawk'' (1974)== This [[Greyhawk (supplement)|first supplement]] to the Gygax/Arneson boxed set is by [[Gary Gygax]] and [[Robert J. Kuntz|Rob Kuntz]] and was printed in 1974. Information is presented in a similar manner as that in the boxed set booklet. Page 33 contains an index of the monsters presented in the book, and pages 34–40 contain descriptions of each monster. Additions and corrections to Vampires and Elementals from the boxed set are included in this book on page 34.
