aping maws flanked by pairs of exceedingly sharp mandibles }} {{D&D creature list |Name=[[Will-o'-Wisp (Dungeons & Dragons)|Will O'Wisp]] |PageNumber=35 |OtherAppearances= |Variants= |Description=Highly clever creatures that lure foes to feed upon their life force }} |}
